42:51Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"MEMBER","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"Over in https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon-website/pull/1245 we received a PR that adds in guidance for nested checkboxes. This issue is for adding an example for this use-case, or for introducing a component that helps tackle this.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6193/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6193/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10285","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10285/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10285/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10285/events","html_url":"https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10285","id":1080180617,"node_id":"I_kwDOBQ58z85AYj-J","number":10285,"title":"[Bug]: Keyboard focus outline of batch checkbox in DataTable header overlaps the next header column","user":{"login":"obambrough","id":1922249,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5MjIyNDk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1922249?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough","html_url":"https://github.com/obambrough","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/obambrough/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1056028595,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMDU2MDI4NTk1","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/type:%20bug%20%F0%9F%90%9B","name":"type: bug üêõ","color":"3ddbd9","default":false,"description":""},{"id":1354806576,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMzU0ODA2NTc2","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/package:%20react","name":"package: react","color":"d4bbff","default":false,"description":"carbon-components-react"},{"id":1692677297,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNjkyNjc3Mjk3","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/component:%20data-table","name":"component: data-table","color":"a6c8ff","default":false,"description":""}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2021-12-14T20:22:19Z","updated_at":"2021-12-15T22:21:38Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"### Package\n\ncarbon-components, carbon-components-react\n\n### Browser\n\nChrome\n\n### Package version\n\nv7.50\n\n### React version\n\nv17.0.2\n\n### Description\n\nThe focus ring of the batch checkbox overlaps with the next column\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1922249/146072337-d2032066-97c9-4f13-9c77-44ac7e53f9b9.png)\r\n\r\nThe above image is from the codesandbox example. The overlap affects our use more as we've modified the header styles to have position sticky - this causes the outline to be clipped:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1922249/146073044-67d9556f-6b74-41c0-8df2-900005226ce9.png)\r\n\r\nI see the vanilla javascript Carbon components have a different keyboard focus compared to the react version:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1922249/146072804-3d6dc3e0-d2e7-40cc-8397-52e026e7e7dc.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\n\n### CodeSandbox example\n\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/carbon-components-react-7-50-datatable-focus-ring-overlap-e1gdr\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nMove keyboard focus to the checkbox in the Datatable header, this shows the focus outline. I've altered the name column's header to be red to highlight the outline is overlapping the name column's header.\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's [Code of Conduct](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/blob/f555616971a03fd454c0f4daea184adf41fff05b/.github/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md)\n- [X] I checked the [current issues](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues) for duplicate problems","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10285/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10285/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6567","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6567/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6567/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6567/events","html_url":"https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6567","id":667000084,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU2NjcwMDAwODQ=","number":6567,"title":"Toggle and ToggleSmall aria-label is better placed on the checkbox, not the label element","user":{"login":"FrivalszkyP","id":3766124,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM3NjYxMjQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3766124?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP","html_url":"https://github.com/FrivalszkyP","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/FrivalszkyP/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1056028613,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMDU2MDI4NjEz","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/type:%20a11y%20%E2%99%BF","name":"type: a11y ‚ôø","color":"3ddbd9","default":false,"description":""},{"id":1692683513,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNjkyNjgzNTEz","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/component:%20toggle","name":"component: toggle","color":"a6c8ff","default":false,"description":""},{"id":2143534559,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyMTQzNTM0NTU5","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/status:%20waiting%20for%20maintainer%20response%20%F0%9F%92%AC","name":"status: waiting for maintainer response üí¨","color":"002d9c","default":false,"description":""},{"id":2218532206,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyMjE4NTMyMjA2","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/screen-reader:%20JAWS","name":"screen-reader: JAWS","color":"FFAFD2","default":false,"description":""}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2020-07-28T11:31:57Z","updated_at":"2021-06-25T18:30:27Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"## Toggle and ToggleSmall aria-labels are misplaced - the attribute should go on the input element, not the label\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n> MacOS\r\n\r\n> Chrome\r\n\r\n> VoiceOver\r\n\r\n## Detailed description\r\n\r\nVoiceOver on Chrome does not announce the aria-label of the Toggle element because the attribute is on the label element, not the input itself.\r\n\r\n> What did you expect to happen?\r\n\r\nI expected the text of the aria-label to be announced by VoiceOver upon focusing on the toggle element.\r\n\r\n> What happened instead?\r\n\r\nThe text was not announced, only the \"tick box\" and its on/off state. \r\n\r\n> What WCAG 2.1 checkpoint does the issue violate?\r\n\r\nLooking at the \"accessible name computation\" specification, it seems to me that the current setup, having an aria-label on a label, is not in the specification. The aria-label attribute would be better suited on the input element itself.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n1. Turn on VoiceOver for Chrome\r\n2. Go to [Storybook](https://react.carbondesignsystem.com/?path=/story/togglesmall--toggled)\r\n2. Navigate to the Toggle element\r\n\r\n## Additional information\r\n\r\n- It's important to note that the label is announced in Safari, which is probably the most used browser with VoiceOver\r\n- I was unable to test this with NVDA/JAWS at the moment\r\n- But as per specification, I thing the aria attribute should go onto the input element anyways. \r\n- I tested it by moving the attribute using the Developer Tools, and it worked both with Safari and Chrome\r\n\r\nLet me know if you found my reasoning solid, and I'll go ahead and create a PR!","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6567/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6567/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/8716","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/8716/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/8716/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/8716/events","html_url":"https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/8716","id":894731218,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU4OTQ3MzEyMTg=","number":8716,"title":"Delay when clicking the select-all checkbox on the Datatable at 500 records. ","user":{"login":"Cahalanb","id":13424679,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzNDI0Njc5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/13424679?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb","html_url":"https://github.com/Cahalanb","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Cahalanb/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1056028595,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMDU2MDI4NTk1","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/type:%20bug%20%F0%9F%90%9B","name":"type: bug üêõ","color":"3ddbd9","default":false,"description":""},{"id":1692677297,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNjkyNjc3Mjk3","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/component:%20data-table","name":"component: data-table","color":"a6c8ff","default":false,"description":""}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2021-05-18T20:01:13Z","updated_at":"2021-05-19T16:14:12Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"## What package(s) are you using?\r\n\r\n- [ ] `carbon-components`\r\n- [ x ] `carbon-components-react`\r\n\r\n## Detailed description\r\nWe have setup a Datatable to display records where Items per page allows for 10, 20 ... 500. Setting this to 500 items per page, attempt to click the select-all checkbox on the column header toolbar. There is a clear delay of about two seconds until the selection is reflected in the table UI. This is for both checking & un-checking.\r\n\r\nThere is also a delay if the user clicks any of the checkboxes at row level.\r\n\r\n\r\n> Is this issue related to a specific component?\r\nDatatable\r\n\r\n> What did you expect to happen? What happened instead? What would you like to\r\n> see changed?\r\nA more timely update of the Datatable to reflect the checkbox selection. Right now, it may appear to the user that no selection was made.\r\n\r\n> What browser are you working in?\r\nChrome Version 90.0.4430.212 (Official Build) (x86_64)\r\n\r\n> What version of the Carbon Design System are you using?\r\n\"@carbon/ibm-security\": \"=1.38.0\",\r\n\r\n> What offering/product do you work on? Any pressing ship or release dates we\r\n> should be aware of?\r\nIBM Cloud Pak for Security - Cases\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n1. Setup a carbon datatable\r\n2. Populate the table with 500 rows ( about 10 columns )\r\n3. Click the select-all checkbox on the column bar at the top of the table\r\n4. Click any of the checkboxes of a particular row.\r\n\r\n> Please create a reduced test case in CodeSandbox\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/codesandbox-forked-bf2lw?file=/src/index.js\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/8716/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/8716/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1}]}}